1. *Ovi* dani su veoma hladni. (These days are very cold.)
2. Njena odjeća bila je *ovih* boja. (Her clothes were these colors.)
3. Nema nikakve sumnje da je *ovi* čovjek nevin. (There is no doubt that this man is innocent.)
4. Ona je izvukla *ove* knjige iz torbe. (She pulled these books out of her bag.)
5. *Ovi* su ljudi vrlo pouzdani. (These people are very reliable.)